Make them notice you everywhere,
so they can't stop thinking about you.

274
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:54,302
[Director's Office]

275
00:19:26,157 --> 00:19:27,432
[Sunho]

276
00:19:51,506 --> 00:19:54,281
